---
layout: layout-base.njk
pagination:
  data: crops
  size: 1
  alias: crop
permalink: "crops/{{ crop.slug }}/"
title: "Growing {{ crop.name }} in Short Growing Seasons | GrowByDate"
description: "{{ crop.description }}"
canonical: "https://growbydate.com/crops/{{ crop.slug }}/"
---

<header class="header">
  <h1>Growing {{ crop.name }} in Short Growing Seasons</h1>
  <p class="tagline">Practical timing and a clear plan—without the hype.</p>
  <p class="lede">{{ crop.description }}</p>
</header>

<section class="card">
  <h2>Quick Planning Reference</h2>
  <ul>
    {% if crop.indoorStartWeeks %}
      <li><strong>Indoor start:</strong> {{ crop.indoorStartWeeks[1] }}–{{ crop.indoorStartWeeks[0] }} weeks before your average last frost</li>
    {% endif %}

    {% if crop.transplantWeeks %}
      {# transplantWeeks: [latest, earliest] or [max, min] depending on crop.
         For warm crops you’ll likely keep both positive (weeks after last frost).
         For cool crops you may use negatives (weeks before last frost).
      #}
      <li><strong>Transplant:</strong>
        {% if crop.transplantWeeks[0] < 0 or crop.transplantWeeks[1] < 0 %}
          {{ crop.transplantWeeks[0] | abs }}–{{ crop.transplantWeeks[1] | abs }} weeks <em>before</em> last frost (weather permitting)
        {% else %}
          {{ crop.transplantWeeks[1] }}–{{ crop.transplantWeeks[0] }} weeks <em>after</em> last frost (once conditions are suitable)
        {% endif %}
      </li>
    {% endif %}

    {% if crop.directSowWeeks %}
      <li><strong>Direct sow:</strong>
        {% if crop.directSowWeeks[0] < 0 or crop.directSowWeeks[1] < 0 %}
          {{ crop.directSowWeeks[0] | abs }}–{{ crop.directSowWeeks[1] | abs }} weeks <em>before</em> last frost
        {% else %}
          {{ crop.directSowWeeks[1] }}–{{ crop.directSowWeeks[0] }} weeks <em>before</em> last frost
        {% endif %}
      </li>
    {% endif %}

    {% if crop.daysToMaturity %}
      <li><strong>Days to maturity:</strong> {{ crop.daysToMaturity[0] }}–{{ crop.daysToMaturity[1] }} days (variety-dependent)</li>
    {% endif %}
    <li><strong>Frost tolerance:</strong> {{ crop.frostTolerance }}</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    To generate exact windows based on your dates, use the
    <a href="/tools/seed-start-planner/">Seed Starting Planner</a>.
  </p>
</section>

{# Optional per-crop notes (drop in a file at _includes/crops/{{ crop.slug }}-notes.md ) #}
{% set notesPath = "crops/" + crop.slug + "-notes.md" %}
{% if (notesPath | fileExists) %}
  <section class="card">
    <h2>Notes for Short Seasons</h2>
    {% include notesPath %}
  </section>
{% endif %}

<section class="card">
  <h2>Related Tools</h2>
  <ul>
    {% for toolId in crop.relatedTools %}
      {% for tool in tools %}
        {% if tool.id == toolId %}
          <li><a href="{{ tool.url }}">{{ tool.name }}</a></li>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</section>

<footer class="footer">
  <p><a href="/crops/">← Back to Crops</a></p>
</footer>
